title: I believe I now understand whats going on with the
message:
I believe I now understand whats going on with the 
cell spacing issue. I am creating a space between the 
inner content view and its encasing cell.
It is this space that is clipping the text, and causing the 
constraint warning.
I think content views should always remain as tall as its parent cell.
And maybe if I need to do cell spacing, I should be looking at
solutions that involve the cell on the outside, and not using tricks
with the content view on the inside.
